---
export const prerender = true;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="pl">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#ffffff" />
    <title>MacroSpy - Brak połączenia</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light dark;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #111827;
        padding: 24px;
      }

      .card {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 480px;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 24px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .actions {
        margin-top: 16px;
        display: flex;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      button {
        border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #111827;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        font: inherit;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        body {
          background: #09090b;
          color: #f4f4f5;
        }

        .card {
          border-color: #27272a;
          background: #18181b;
        }

        button {
          border-color: #3f3f46;
          background: #27272a;
          color: #f4f4f5;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="card">
      <h1>Brak połączenia z internetem</h1>
      <p>Nie udało się załadować tej strony. Sprawdź połączenie i spróbuj ponownie za chwilę.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <button type="button" onclick="window.location.reload()">Spróbuj ponownie</button>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
